_sText:
The map has a very exciting structure. With teleports, different height level, and many variables, it is very funny to play. It has some colors, and it has three basic texture. I called it deathroom, because my inspiration was the Half-Life 2: DM map "dm_killbox". I love this map. Many good sniper spots, many ways to hide from the sniper spots, some hidden ways and secrets.
It works as a GunGame map, a FY, Aim, skill-training, combat, etc.

Please let me know if you are going to host you map on your server, I would love to play this map online with gamers from all over the world!

ENJ0y!
